## Frontmatter Schema (`london-uk.mdx` as reference)
```yaml
slug, title, excerpt, date, dateModified, author
region, regionCode, language, locale, city, country
canonical, targetKeyword, secondaryKeywords, searchIntent, noIndex
tldr                    # 40-60 word answer capsule shown in hero
faqSchema               # array of { question, answer }
entityType, speakable
contact:
  email, whatsapp, instagram
services:               # array of { title, description }
schemaType              # "ProfessionalService" | "LocalBusiness"
template: business
image, imageAlt, imageWidth, imageHeight
galleryImages:          # array of { url, alt, width, height }
```

---

## JSON-LD Schemas (injected in `[slug]/page.tsx`)
1. `ProfessionalService` — with `areaServed`, `hasOfferCatalog` (one per service)
2. `FAQPage` — from `faqSchema` frontmatter array
3. `BreadcrumbList` — Home → Business → Region
4. `Speakable` — if `speakable: true` in frontmatter

