## SEO / GEO / AEO Notes
- One MDX file per region = one page, zero code changes needed
- `hreflang` via `regionCode` + `alternates.languages` in `generateMetadata`
- `noIndex` frontmatter field respected in robots meta
- OG type: `website` (not `article`)
- TL;DR in hero = 40–60 word extractable answer capsule for AI search engines
- FAQ schema = highest-ROI GEO move

